a fantastic product that can help users with goal setting and stress management. But sometimes people need a push. With Bellabeat's bio-response tracking, users can get even more in tuned with their bodies through helpful reminders on their watch or on the app that can encourage users to move more throughout the day and achieve their goals.\n","\n","3.  **How could these trends help influence Bellabeat marketing strategy?**\n","\n","-   The [Center for Disease Control recommends](https://www.cdc.gov/physicalactivity/basics/adults/index.htm) at least \"150 minutes of moderate-intensity physical activity\" each week. Push notifications are a great way to remind users to get up and get moving. Targeted exercises can change with how well users are or are not meeting their goals and premium users can tap intoeven more personalized coaching with awareness of how much more exercise they're getting. With menstrual cycle and heart rate tracking, push notifications can be helpful reminders to get blood flowing, which can improve mood and overall physical health.\n","\n","# Appendix\n","\n","## Tables\n","\n","#### **Average Total Steps**"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","id":"6fcf9357","metadata":{"papermill":{"duration":0.010307,"end_time":"2023-10-05T13:40:34.173685","exception":false,"start_time":"2023-10-05T13:40:34.163378","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"source":["<table>\n","<thead>\n","  <tr>\n","    <th>participant ID number</th>\n","    <th>total steps</th>\n","    <th>total distance</th>\n","    <th>tracker distance</th>\n","    <th>logged activities distance</th>\n","    <th>very active distance</th>\n","    <th>moderatelyactive distance</th>\n","    <th>light active distance</th>\n","    <th>sedentary<br>active distance</th>\n","    <th>very active mins</th>\n","    <th>fairly active mins</th>\n","    <th>lightly active mins</th>\n","    <th>sedentary<br>mins</th>\n","    <th>calories</th>\n","  </tr>\n","</thead>\n","<tbody>\n","  <tr>\n","    <td>8877689391</td>\n",